        "desc": "This small flet glitters and sparkles in the light. On display in cabinets are\nluxurious items, crafted by the last of the great artisans from the old Noldorin\ncity of Ost-in-Edhil. Wooden shelves and work benches are placed in a\nsemi-circle around a small stone hearth that stands off towards a corner. Tiny\nflames dance in the fireplace, allowing the smiths to heat and work their\nmaterial to perfection. A couple of wooden chests and a table are placed along\nthe edge of the flet. In a corner are a few sleeping mats.\n",
