    {
        "desc": "The great platform lies firm against the thick branches of the mallorn, not\nmoving even as gusts of winds sway the smaller branches. A narrow wooden railing\nruns all around the platform. The most prominent feature in sight is the great\nhall that lies on the northern part of the flet, although several other features\nattract attention. The polished floor is covered with beautiful carvings inlaid\nwith silver strands that glitter in vivid patterns, reflecting light from a\nmyriad of silver lamps and sending it to dance among the branches. The railing\nis meticulously crafted out of the finest wood by the finest artisans. It seems\ndelicate yet is strong and supportive, just like the elves themselves.\n",
