    {
        "desc": "One of the highest places in the realm of the Golden Wood is the chamber of the\nLord and Lady of Lothlorien - Celeborn of the Teleri and Galadriel of the\nNoldor. Small but carefully furnished, the chamber is decorated by some of the\nfinest artefacts created by the great artisans of the history of Arda. On the\nwalls hang several beautiful gems, reflecting the light of several silver lamps.\nA small sapling of the great silver tree, whose name was given to the ruler of\nCaras Galadhon, stands here on a small silver pedestal. A large bed stands on\nthe side, covered by draping in sky-blue and white hanging from the ceiling.\n",
